[SN]TITLE[SN]
Would the UK be better off in or out the EU?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Would the UK be better off financially in or out of the European Union? That was the subject of a BBC Newsnight special on Monday night.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Click here to watch and follow a live blog of the programme
Last week, Newsnight explored the question of sovereignty - and asked "Who really rules the UK?"
The programmes are part of a series of Newsnight specials unpacking the big questions behind the UK's referendum vote on 23 June.
Next Monday, the subject will be "Security - Would the UK be safer in or out the EU?"
